org.escoladeltreball.ulisesmap.activities

Class MapActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • org.escoladeltreball.ulisesmap.activities.BaseActivity
        • org.escoladeltreball.ulisesmap.activities.MapActivity

  • public class MapActivity
extends BaseActivity
    MapActivity Show a route from an array of points according to chosen option in menu. Depending on activity that started this one an array of points may be ordered for improve a result route The different options handled by this activity lets to show changes on the map at run time, like route type, navigation marker o user location.
